%2FgxRwqJX.png&h=f2693a69&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n講得好 連登就係多得佢 木耳 飲L乜撚M依幾條<strong><strong><span class=\"red\">當連登係FB玩嘅死狗公</span></strong></strong>唔少<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OoZJ1iP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOoZJ1iP.jpg&h=ab6c268d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qQcSUDQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqQcSUDQ.png&h=7000e983&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 恥笑毒撚 佢主人濟癲 老死浮雲 多次恥笑毒撚 話毒撚社會垃圾 反社會人渣 同依班人為伍嘅會員#370062都唔好得去邊 明明自己都係毒撚 正一25仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FYD3gS1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFYD3gS1.png&h=ac29add3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/brgsJxB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbrgsJxB.png&h=0d69bccc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UDk9crV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUDk9crV.png&h=8b94f1f5&s={SIZE}\" />"}}